Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, it wasn't your fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just did what you had to do as a doctor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't your fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the sandwiches\Nand get some rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to survive,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and save as many people as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina Fortner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina... What do you intend to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you intend to try to kill him again?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought him back to life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}brought that monster{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}back to life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This arteriovenous malformation contains many blood vessels...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut away all of the inflowing arteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat all of the outflowing veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal of the nidus is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... that certainly went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He did the clipping\Nvery quickly, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a magnificent operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his first surgery after\Nan extended leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but the talent of this genius\Nkeeps growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was wonderful, Kenzo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wasn't news about me,\Nbut about your father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's true...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's because you did such a perfect job last night, as part of Father's team.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure Father is grateful to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, you're the one who has\Nraised the fame of the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one who is grateful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's thanks to your father that\NI am able to work here in Germany.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there, Kenzo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you stick with Father,\Nyour future is guaranteed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It won't be long before Father\Nbecomes Chairman of the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then you'll quickly become\NChief of Surgery,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and in time, Hospital Director...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, I will be the Director's wife!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must make me happy, now.\NHardships do not become me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You want to go out on a date?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm afraid you cannot...\NThe mistress is resting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take much of her time.\NI will leave very shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, please return again\Nafter making an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm terribly sorry, Ma'am.\NIt's the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again,\NMiss Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for the help you gave me\Non your father's case, nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lunge of the Federal Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave us, Horst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just a useless detective\Nwho couldn't even close that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been able to maintain this residence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,even after your father's death.\NI am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I do believe all of the furnishing\Nis even grander than it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to see how wealthy\NI've become with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,my inheritance from my father\Nand settlements from my divorces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I lack nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see anything you want\Nplease help yourself to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, as long as I have my liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Today... I would like you to have a look at something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something from nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple print,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you look at it carefully, it's a wonderful piece with a complex weave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This really gave me a hard time.\NAfter all, it's been nine years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But luckily, this comes from a shop\Nthat had a limited number of these
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,made for their best customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And on their list...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I found your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you purchase this\Nand give it to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This plays a key role\Nin another murder, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given countless gifts to men,\Nso I can't remember them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The men who approach me\Nare all after my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all after my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a single person\Nwho truly loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I took each one\Nto the cleaners with each divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You want something? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember it'll cost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remember anything,\Nplease give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you come,\Nbe sure to bring a bottle of liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva, won't you talk to\Nyour father for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't done anything wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just operated on an emergency case in the order in which he was brought in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's... your engagement ring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're such a fool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why, Dr. Norden,\Ndon't you look elegant?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As do you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're more beautiful than ever tonight, Eva.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Horst, have my car readied!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Hess, you seem to be much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your color is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll be able to go home\Nsometime this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter is getting married next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to attend her wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't overdo it at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I had resigned myself to not going,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but thanks to you, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was due to your own efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With you at my side,\NI feel as though I can be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,not only at my daughter's,\Nbut at my grand children's weddings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly an excellent doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay here at this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Dr. Tenma... You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I must make my rounds now.\NI'm too busy. Please turn them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gone through so much,\Nhaven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father... Are you asleep?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm coming in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it's hard, but you must\Npull yourself together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let go of me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give me back my father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenzo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, I was wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenzo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenzo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost some weight, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you were on extended leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you should rest yourself\Nfrom time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a glutton for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost some weight too,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So much has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard the rumors,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring... Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, in spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We often went driving together...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to swim in the river\Nin that season...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurriedly stopped you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, I haven't got time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After three failed marriages,\NI finally realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the only one who truly loved me\Nwas you, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just can't accept them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kenzo! I didn't say a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When the police came\Nto ask about your necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something bad\Nconnected with that necktie of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's the tie that I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do as I say,\NI'll keep quiet about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the police about that necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who killed my father\Nnine years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Bring Dr. Tenma in\Nas a person of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But there isn't enough evidence in the Fortner couple and Maurer murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about\Nthe killing at Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This might allow us\Nto solve a lot of murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Resignation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this,\NDr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I'm acting selfishly, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There seem to be various\Nstrange rumors about you, recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't believe any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think this over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... T-Tenma!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is a murder suspect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Close off the exits from each wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the back exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on there?\NHurry up and search the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're interfering with the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma would never kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're indebted to him\Nfor saving our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seems to be going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:19:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole bunch\Nof patrol cars, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see... I wonder what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just drop me off\Nin front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy as always,\Naren't you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I have a surgery waiting for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait! Dr. Tenma!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll save you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am not wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You say there's\Na flaw in my character?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You call yourself a doctor,\Nbut you're just money hungry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bastard... That bastard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's better off dead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The twins are nowhere to be found!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Long time no see, Doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you already forgotten\Nabout those twins?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Save me, Doctor... I don't want to die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was supposed to have died that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You brought me back to life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like another scorcher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's summer, yet you're all\Nbundled up. Aren't you hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?\NThat paper's three days old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They say this time a middle-aged couple\Nin Verden was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the killer is a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... You said you're going\Nto Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can meet up with him or not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.79,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:44.26,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:53.64,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:59.28,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:07.07,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:16.17,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.46,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:28.26,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:33.14,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting
